# Assets Loans And Receivables Calls For Additional Insurance Premiums Amount

## identifier
de8995

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of calls receivable for additional contribution revenue. This is made by the governing body to cover a wide range of circumstances such as exposure to additional risk, to cover cost of default.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.LoansAndReceivables.CallsForAdditionalInsurancePremiums.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo5.02.06
- period=instant
